headline: Sysco Addresses Food Insecurity in Global Communities, Exceeding Its Giving Goals in 3rd Annual Purpose Month
summary: Thousands of Sysco colleagues volunteered 36,817 hours in November to help ease global food insecurity, impacting over 1,700 individual charities HOUSTON, TX / ACCESS Newswire / December 18, 2025 /Originally published on December 16, 2025 on Sysco.com ...
